    {
        "content": "<p>Thank you, I see now that I have to learn more about the <code>with</code> clause in <code>rcases</code>.  I eventually arrived at something similar (non solution), with this pattern:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hm</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">all_goals</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">obtain</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"bp\">|</span><span class=\"n\">h₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">...</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I was thinking that, if there isn't one already, maybe a macro could automate this business: <code>( · | · | · | ⋯ | · |)</code></p>",
